dct_title_s: Jinan tourist map = 济南导游图
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Includes 5 ancillary maps: Daminghu Park--Baotuquan Park--Qianfoshan Park--Qufu--Mount Taishan. Selected buildings are shown pictorially. Tourist information on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Beijing, China : Cartographic Publishing House : distributed by China Publications Centre, 1983.
